OL,3,CEmployees and police officers hurt in
OL,4,Csledgehammer attack at business park
OL,6,FA targeted attack on a Bristol
OL,7,Fbusiness has seen employees ambushed
OL,8,Fwith weapons and police officers hurt
OL,9,Fwith a sledgehammer.
OL,11,FPolice were called to what they
OL,12,Finitially thought was a burglary in
OL,13,FBolingbroke Way, Patchway, at around
OL,14,F4am on Tuesday 6 August.
OL,16,FA large vehicle had been driven
OL,17,Fthrough the property's fence before it
OL,18,Fwas used to ram the building's
OL,19,Fentrance.
