OL,3,CEmployees and police officers hurt in
OL,4,Csledgehammer attack at business park
OL,6,FPolice say more than a dozen people
OL,7,Fthen got out of the vehicle and began
OL,8,Fto damage the building. Employees who
OL,9,Ftried to intervene were then attacked
OL,10,Fwith weapons.
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police arrived at
OL,13,Fthe scene within minutes. Six people
OL,14,Fhave been arrested.
OL,16,FTwo police officers were assaulted
OL,17,Fwith a sledgehammer - one was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital with back injuries while the
OL,19,Fother treated at the scene by
OL,20,Fparamedics for injuries to the back of
OL,21,Fhis legs.
