OL,3,CEmployees and police officers hurt in
OL,4,Csledgehammer attack at business park
OL,6,FAt least one of the firm's employees
OL,7,Fwas also treated at the scene for an
OL,8,Finjury to their head.
OL,10,FPolice say sledgehammers, axes, whips
OL,11,Fand other homemade weapons were found
OL,12,Fat the scene.
OL,14,FSuperintendent Paul Wigginton said:
OL,15,F"This is a disturbing incident
OL,16,Finvolving people willing to use
OL,17,Fsignificant violence against anyone
OL,18,Fwho got in their way as they targeted
OL,19,Fthis business.
