OL,3,CEmployees and police officers hurt in
OL,4,Csledgehammer attack at business park
OL,6,F"The criminal damage is bad enough but
OL,7,Fto attack people with weapons is
OL,8,Foutrageous.
OL,10,F"Some of those involved were able to
OL,11,Fflee the scene but detectives are
OL,12,Falready working hard to bring them
OL,13,Finto custody.
OL,15,F"There is no justification whatsoever
OL,16,Ffor what happened and those
OL,17,Fresponsible will face severe
OL,18,Fconsequences."
