OL,3,CEmployees and police officers hurt in
OL,4,Csledgehammer attack at business park
OL,6,FHe said the responding officers
OL,7,Fdemonstrated "great courage" when
OL,8,Ffaced with armed offenders, adding:
OL,9,F"It is a sad fact that officers now
OL,10,Fexpect to face acts of violence as
OL,11,Fthey respond to crimes in action and
OL,12,Fprotect the public.
OL,14,F"This is completely unacceptable and
OL,15,Fanyone responsible for such shameful
OL,16,Fbehaviour can expect to go to prison."
